# This directory contains secrets - DO NOT COMMIT actual key files
#
# Required files:
#   master-key.txt - 32-byte hex key for credential encryption
#   api-key.txt    - 32-byte hex key for Bearer token auth
#
# Generate with:
#   openssl rand -hex 32 > master-key.txt
#   openssl rand -hex 32 > api-key.txt
#   chmod 600 *.txt
